setAuctionBidder.t.sol
├─ when the caller does not have the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the caller has the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
   ├─ when the auction bidder is set to the zero address
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the auction bidder is not set to the zero address
      ├─ when the new auction bidder does not support the IAuctionBidder interface
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when the new auction bidder supports the IAuctionBidder interface
         ├─ when the new auction bidder is the same address as the already configured one
         │  └─ it should revert
         └─ when the new auction bidder is different than the already configured one
            ├─ it should set the new auction bidder
            └─ it should emit a AuctionBidderSet event
